        Finds the ResourceName of the resource with the given name, relative to our current workspace.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the resource to find.
        resolveName - true if the name is a variable that we may need to resolve first.
        Returns:

        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - If the resource cannot be found.
